  <span id="freeText14923164832881644738" style="display:none">Caroline Kepnes is the New York Times bestselling author of You, Hidden Bodies, Providence and... <br /><br />You Love Me. Publishing in the US on Aril 6, 2021<br /><br />(You know You Netflix? That's based on my Joe Goldberg books! You can read You3 before Season 3)<br /><br />Her work has been translated into a multitude of languages and inspired a television series adaptation of You, currently on Netflix. Kepnes graduated from Brown University and then worked as a pop culture journalist for Entertainment Weekly and a TV writer for 7th Heaven and The Secret Life of the American Teenager. She grew up on Cape Cod, and now lives in Los Angeles.<br /> </span>
